571,"uid":28002,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T20:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就係你依啲女人麻撚煩</blockquote><br />\n咁你想點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收埋係唔會解決到問題<br />\n兩個人相處係需要溝通先會向好果邊發展<br />\n<br />\n你應該講你嬲既原因係乜 跟住慢慢解決問題<br />\n乜都唔講基本上同等散無乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d76a4976c8c71d5f664a159728c1cd6b05f982f","tid":311571,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T21:00:17.000Z","msg":"樓主係嬲緊先唔講嘢  事後傾返？<br />\n過左啖氣先傾幾好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4223f508dcb88bf0406d699d5d37deecce399605","tid":311571,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T21:00:33.000Z","msg":"唔出聲一定好過個下就發鳩你脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩咪下左啖氣先傾<br />\n唔覺有咩問題"},{"pid":"7dbd2e48b2fa3e3533aa2c137dc0e1a292d2855b","tid":311571,"uid":113380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係咁<br />\n但反而人地仲嬲<br />\n我每次一唔出聲<br />\n佢屌得仲西利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c422b5247ec2ffe0293c5741ec39fde006bc7cab","tid":311571,"uid":113380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係嬲緊先唔講嘢  事後傾返？<br />\n過左啖氣先傾幾好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係囉"},{"pid":"7f9a3517e1a37848cb545b8c6f1d7caf9e114009","tid":311571,"uid":113380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我開頭會嬲到唔想理佢 跟住愈諗愈嬲就屌9佢<br />\n但重複既錯就屌都費事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔會屌9佢 因為唔識表達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f807b9c7fef40964972d3c1db8c8c25f3b2a84a","tid":311571,"uid":113380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:12:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔出聲一定好過個下就發鳩你脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩咪下左啖氣先傾<br />\n唔覺有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n佢就係覺得係一齊既時間唔應該粒聲唔出<br />\n曬曬一齊既時間<br />\n同埋佢覺得男女朋友唔應該好似陌生人咁粒聲唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d606237ccedb3e28b90e5ea5ad840f227afb48f","tid":311571,"uid":6957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T04:26:44.000Z","msg":"我男朋友同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同你男朋友一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25785bb53c46b9b191757af24f47b8209874a975","tid":311571,"uid":113380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我男朋友同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同你男朋友一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係男同女調轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢兩句野睇左幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc1472aa53e47e9fde9dc440911eb258b2e41ad","tid":311571,"uid":73152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:25:22.000Z","msg":"我女朋友一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嬲緊點好聲好氣應你呀"},{"pid":"f6c94b3bd0882b97c24bc0ec051771f5c0b2ffa9","tid":311571,"uid":107043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T20:25:44.000Z","msg":"LM我近期都諗緊呢樣野...<br />\n我唔係個啲嬲就唔出聲既人 好多時會直接講自己有咩嬲就發脾氣 但我知每次發脾氣都會令關係傷害到 所以好想好想收晒自己啲脾氣 <br />\n但次次比時間自己冷靜完 同自己講左唔可以發脾氣 一同佢講番野又會嬲番 搞到好唔開心<br />\n其實我覺得正常係有不和既時候應該係大家靜下冷靜左先 咁樣最衝動既說話先唔會講到出口 冷靜黎大家講番發生咩事 點解會唔開心同雙方既感受 最後就你氹我氹和好左 咁樣先係好既溝通（對我黎講）"},{"pid":"40e13edf1542f67b2619bfd606614dcbd0e3ba4c","tid":311571,"uid":46061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T00:22:14.000Z","msg":"嬲個陣咪講句想靜下<br />\n等我心情平復啲再講<br />\n起碼比人知咩事唔出聲先"},{"pid":"69d11f987c4334f39e7470e1c3fb16c8331fc586","tid":311571,"uid":6957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:47:14.000Z","msg":"我覺得冷暴力先最傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e096d3591ffec5d79c9e664e3b0cefae2a27c2e0","tid":311571,"uid":9368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:48:40.000Z","msg":"等下次氣氛好少少時候講，其實上次咁樣我好嬲"}]}